net.ashwork.upvote.domain

Interface UserEntry<USER>

  • Type Parameters:
    USER - the type of the user
    All Known Subinterfaces:
    ReputationEntry<USER,REPUTATION,TIME>, VoteEntry<USER,ITEM,VOTE,TIME>

    public interface UserEntry<USER>
    A helper that specifies that a particular object entry has a user with some type.
    Since:
    1.0.0
    API Note:
    The type of the user can be an object wrapper of a composite type. This just specifies that it defines what a user is within the entry.
